92. Apply the various steps involved to get cookie value using server-side scripting.
code:
<?php
// Step 1: Set a cookie (expires in 1 hour)
setcookie("user", "JohnDoe", time() + 3600, "/");

// Step 2 & 3: Read the cookie
echo "<h3>Cookie Example</h3>";

if(isset($_COOKIE['user'])) {
    echo "Cookie 'user' value: " . $_COOKIE['user'];
} else {
    echo "Cookie 'user' is not set yet. Refresh the page.";
}
?>
